The designs and words that customers see are inseparable. Together, they help us build and maintain a connection with customers.

These guidelines aim to help us write in a way that helps our customers successfully complete their task online in the quickest and simplest way possible.

### These guidelines will change

Customers’ needs evolve, so these guidelines will change to keep up with those requirements. Often, we won’t get things right the first time, but we can get better after each iteration.
